    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 13 V&V 40 credibility factors assessed. Twelve of thirteen factors meet or exceed the required credibility level. The single below-requirement factor (Test conditions, achieved 2 vs. required 3) is mitigated by the conservative nature of the ASTM F1717 protocol and the direct regulatory relevance of the single test configuration. Quantitative comparison metrics (E/uval <1.96, percent differences <10%) are satisfied for all three QoIs across two independent laboratories. The overall credibility evidence is sufficient to support the Accepted decision for regulatory submission.",
